<body>
    <%- include("common/navbar") %>

    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="container fadein-left">
            <h1>about us</h1>
            <p>
                Soundbites is a news site and blog based around music, which publishes “bite-sized” articles.
                Our goal is to encourage music enjoyers of all kinds - regardless of writing skill - to come together and share their thoughts on what they love.
                <br>
                <br>
                We write articles that analyze lyrical and sonic elements of all types of music, including current releases, retrospectives 
                (looks on older, significant albums that changed a certain genre), and give updates on notable events in the music industry.
            </p>
